cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper deals with natural language processing and classification of Twitter accounts based on their text content. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper deals with social media and the detection of automated accounts, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). The paper also involves machine learning and classification, which could fall under cs.CY (Computational Geometry) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
